                       "seoTitle":  "2024 TIN Report | TIN – Technology Investment Network",
                       "body":  "Marking its 20th anniversary, the 2024 Technology Investment Network (TIN) Report offers a comprehensive analysis of New Zealand\u0027s top tech exporters in Hi-tech Manufacturing, ICT, and Biotechnology. This landmark edition showcases the performance of the country\u0027s 200 leading tech firms, providing crucial insights into sector dynamics, regional impacts, and key markets. The report features in-depth analysis of company performance and growth trends, detailed profiles of top 200 companies, and a spotlight on 100 emerging Kiwi tech start-ups. It also includes analysis of primary and secondary sector performance and regional trends, offering a holistic view of the industry. As the definitive resource for New Zealand\u0027s tech ecosystem, the 2024 TIN Report is invaluable for investors, business leaders, policymakers, and anyone interested in the future of the country\u0027s innovation-driven economy. See inside the 2024 TIN Report. Buy Now",
